<P>
   ACCUSED OF STRIKE PLOT, 40 INMATES ARE MOVED
</P>
<P>
   A8629 BC-EXP-CALIF-TOBACCO-NYT 385 21:41 U A
</P>
<P>
   CALIFORNIA TREASURER FAVORS SHEDDING OF TOBACCO STOCKS
</P>
<P>
   A8628 BC-EXP-GAYS-MILITARY-NYT 455 21:39 U A
</P>
<P>
   GAY RIGHTS ADVOCATES AIM TO UNDO `DON'T ASK, DON'T TELL' POLICY
