<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EXCESS-REVIEW-ART-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ON THE TRAIL OF THE SABLE AND LEARJET SET 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: N.Y., R.I., Conn., Fla., Nev., Calif.)  (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036.) 
(The Week in Review) 
