<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-25 17:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8931 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-THISWEEK-REVIEW-NYT &LR;      12-25 1173
