stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Dec. 26 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BKN-LAKERS-SPURS (Los Angeles) _ The Los Angeles Lakers face the
San Antonio Spurs at 6:30 p.m. PST. 
By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKN-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column from Lakers-Spurs game. 
By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKC-UCLA (Los Angeles) _ UCLA basketball post-Hawaii tournament
