<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-25 22:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9165 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s BC-GEN-KEISSER-COLUMN-LA     12-25 1350
